About
=====

- Manipulation of formula and expressions involving
  Boolean, enumerated, bounded integer variables,
  using BDDs

- BDDs as an "abstract" domain

Required
========
C  libraries: 
  CUDD (http://vlsi.colorado.edu/~fabio/CUDD/)
C/OCaml libraries
  mlcuddidl (http://gforge.inria.fr/projects/mlxxxidl/)
OCaml libraries
  camllib (http://gforge.inria.fr/projects/bjeannet/)

To configure
============
- copy Makefile.config.model into Makefile.config
- set properly the flags (mainly directories).

To compile the library:
=======================
make all        # for bytecode and nativecode compilation of formula
make formulatop # for a custom toplevel
make formularun # for a custom bytecode interpreter
make formula.pdf # doc
make html        # doc
...

see Makefile

To install the library:
=======================
make install
